oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Jones, Grandpa, 1913-1998; Shepard, Jean, 1933-2016; Jim and Jesse; Jim and Jesse and the Virginia Boys (Musical group); Virginia Boys; Robbins, Ronny; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and blue on white) announcing Grandpa Jones, Jean Shepard, Jim and Jesse and the Virginia Boys, Ronnie Robbins, and the Second Fiddles at Mattoon Lakeland College on April 3. Poster features metal photoplates of Grandpa Jones, Jean Shepard, and Jim and Jesse. To see the business record associated with this poster, visit https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/43766/
